      <a href="#overview">概述</a>
      <a href="#flows">流程</a>
      <a href="#architecture">架构</a>
      <a href="#modules">模块</a>
      <a href="#prototypes">原型</a>
      <a href="#roles">权限</a>
      <a href="#rules">规范</a>
      <a href="#design">方案</a>
      <a href="#ai-guide">AI 开发</a>
      <a href="#aisummary">评审决策</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</nav>

<header class="hero">
  <div class="container">
    <span class="hero-meta">
      <span class="pulse"></span>
      首次评审 · 文档版本 1.0.0 · 2026-07-09
    </span>
    <h1>NPS 问卷投放<br/><span class="accent">精准投放 · 低打扰 · 数据闭环</span></h1>
    <p class="lead">通过 CSI 系统或运营管理后台制定 NPS 问卷投放计划，由 GAC APP 服务端按国家、车型、绑车时长精准筛选车主并分配问卷链接，在车控页以低打扰浮标触达用户，收集满意度与推荐意愿数据并回流至 CSI 系统形成闭环。</p>
    <div class="hero-cta">
      <a class="btn" href="#overview">
        <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5"><path d="M5 12h14M13 5l7 7-7 7"/></svg>
        开始评审
      </a>
      <a class="btn btn-ghost" href="#" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
        <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M12 .5C5.65.5.5 5.65.5 12c0 5.08 3.29 9.39 7.86 10.91.58.1.79-.25.79-.56v-2.06c-3.2.7-3.87-1.36-3.87-1.36-.52-1.33-1.27-1.69-1.27-1.69-1.04-.71.08-.7.08-.7 1.15.08 1.76 1.18 1.76 1.18 1.02 1.76 2.69 1.25 3.35.96.1-.74.4-1.25.72-1.54-2.55-.29-5.23-1.27-5.23-5.66 0-1.25.45-2.27 1.18-3.07-.12-.29-.51-1.46.11-3.04 0 0 .96-.31 3.15 1.17.91-.25 1.89-.38 2.86-.38.97 0 1.95.13 2.86.38 2.19-1.48 3.15-1.17 3.15-1.17.62 1.58.23 2.75.11 3.04.74.8 1.18 1.82 1.18 3.07 0 4.4-2.68 5.37-5.24 5.65.41.36.77 1.06.77 2.13v3.16c0 .31.21.67.8.56 4.56-1.52 7.85-5.83 7.85-10.91C23.5 5.65 18.35.5 12 .5z"/></svg>
        查看仓库
      </a>
    </div>

    <div class="hero-stats">
      <div class="hero-stat clr-blue">
        <div class="hero-stat-value">5</div>
        <div class="hero-stat-label">功能模块</div>
        <div class="hero-stat-sub">1.1.1 投放计划管理 ~ 1.1.5 问卷页</div>
      </div>
      <div class="hero-stat clr-orange">
        <div class="hero-stat-value">36</div>
        <div class="hero-stat-label">业务规则 BR</div>
        <div class="hero-stat-sub">BR-1.1.1-01 ~ BR-1.1.5-06</div>
      </div>
      <div class="hero-stat clr-green">
        <div class="hero-stat-value">45</div>
        <div class="hero-stat-label">验收标准 AC</div>
        <div class="hero-stat-sub">覆盖正常 · 异常 · 边界三类</div>
      </div>
      <div class="hero-stat clr-purple">
        <div class="hero-stat-value">3</div>
        <div class="hero-stat-label">核心实体</div>
        <div class="hero-stat-sub">投放计划 / 问卷链接 / 投放记录</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</header>

<div class="container">


<!-- ============================================================ -->
<!-- §1 OVERVIEW                                                   -->
<!-- ============================================================ -->
<section id="overview">
  <div class="section-header">
    <div>
      <div class="section-eyebrow"><span class="section-eyebrow-dot"></span> §1 Overview</div>
      <h2 class="section-title">产品概述</h2>
      <p class="section-subtitle">NPS 问卷投放系统核心价值与关键概念</p>
    </div>
    <span class="section-side-meta">5 模块 · 36 BR · 45 AC</span>
  </div>
  <div class="grid grid-2">
    <div class="card clr-red">
      <div class="card-header">
        <div class="card-icon"><svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.2"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><path d="M12 8v4M12 16h.01"/></svg></div>
        <h3 class="card-title">核心问题</h3>
      </div>
      <div class="card-desc">1. 如何按国家、车型、绑车时长精准投放 NPS 问卷？<br>2. 如何在 App 端以低打扰方式触达车主并控制显示频率？<br>3. 如何实现 CSI 系统与 App 服务端的数据闭环？</div>
    </div>
    <div class="card clr-green">
      <div class="card-header">
        <div class="card-icon"><svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.2"><path d="M5 12l5 5L20 7"/></svg></div>
        <h3 class="card-title">核心目标</h3>
      </div>
      <div class="card-desc">1. 支持按多维条件精准筛选目标车主并按比例分配问卷链接。<br>2. 在 App 端以浮标形式低打扰触达用户，支持灵活的显示频率控制。<br>3. 打通 CSI 与 App 服务端的数据链路，实现计划下发、数据回流、完成状态更新。</div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <h3 style="font-size:1.05rem;font-weight:600;margin:2rem 0 1rem;">关键特性</h3>
  <div class="card clr-blue">
    <div class="feature-tags">
      <span class="feature-tag clr-slate">🎯 精准分层投放</span>
      <span class="feature-tag clr-slate">📊 按比例分配问卷</span>
      <span class="feature-tag clr-slate">🔌 CSI 数据闭环</span>
      <span class="feature-tag clr-slate">⏰ 凌晨定时下发</span>
      <span class="feature-tag clr-slate">📱 车控页低打扰浮标</span>
      <span class="feature-tag clr-slate">🔄 显示频率冷却控制</span>
      <span class="feature-tag clr-slate">🌐 WebView H5 容器</span>
      <span class="feature-tag clr-slate">🛡 逻辑删除审计</span>
    </div>
  </div>
  <h3 style="font-size:1.05rem;font-weight:600;margin:2rem 0 1rem;">目标用户</h3>
  <div class="grid grid-3">
    <!-- REPEAT:user_role -->
    <div class="card card-hover clr-{{ROLE_COLOR}}">
      <div class="card-header">
        <div class="card-icon"><svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.2"><circle cx="12" cy="8" r="4"/><path d="M4 21v-2a6 6 0 0 1 6-6h4a6 6 0 0 1 6 6v2"/></svg></div>
        <h3 class="card-title">{{ROLE_NAME}}</h3>
      </div>
      <div class="card-desc">{{ROLE_DESC}}</div>
    </div>
    <!-- /REPEAT -->
  </div>
  <h3 style="font-size:1.05rem;font-weight:600;margin:2rem 0 1rem;">术语表</h3>
  <div class="table-wrap">
    <table>
      <thead><tr><th style="width:10rem;">术语</th><th style="width:11rem;">英文</th><th>定义</th><th style="width:14rem;">备注</th></tr></thead>
      <tbody>
        <!-- REPEAT:term -->
        <tr>
          <td><strong>{{TERM_CN}}</strong></td>
          <td><code>{{TERM_EN}}</code></td>
          <td style="color:var(--fg);">{{TERM_DEF}}</td>
          <td style="color:var(--fg-muted);font-size:0.825rem;">{{TERM_NOTE}}</td>
        </tr>
        <!-- /REPEAT -->
      </tbody>
    </table>
  </div>
</section>

